99-0388 (La. 4/1/99)

Oather HORN v. ILLINOIS INSURANCE EXCHANGE, et al. No. 99-C-0388. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Horn, Oather; — Plaintiffs); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Parish of Rapides 9th Judicial District Court Div. “C” Number 186,148; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98-0573

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J., and LEMMON and KNOLL, JJ. would grant the writ. KIMBALL, J. not on panel.
